declarations.comments: A method to help find the first layer in this document which has the given id.
declarations.title: getLayerWithID

declarations.comments: A method to set value for the path in layer in this document which has the given id.
declarations.title: setPropsForLayerID

declarations.comments: Gets the value of a Sketch setting for a given key.
declarations.title: globalSettingForKey

declarations.comments: Stores a value of a Sketch setting for a given key.
declarations.title: setGlobalSettingForKey

declarations.comments: Gets the value of a setting scoped to your plugin for a given key.
declarations.title: settingForKey

declarations.comments: Stores a value of a setting scoped to your plugin for a given key.

declarations.comments:
Gets the value of a variable which is persisted
when the plugin finishes to run but is not persisted when Sketch closes. 
It is useful when you want to keep a value between plugin’s runs.
declarations.title: sessionVariable

declarations.comments:
Store a value of a variable which is persisted
when the plugin finishes to run but is not persisted when Sketch closes.
It is useful when you want to keep a value between plugin’s runs.
declarations.title: setSessionVariable

declarations.comments: Show an alert with a custom title and message.
declarations.title: alert

declarations.comments: Show a small, temporary, message to the user.
declarations.title: message

declarations.comments:
Shows a simple input sheet which displays a message, 
and asks for an input from the user.
declarations.title: getInputFromUser
